data.description: The Rundle from our Cottage Collection features an open concept living space with 3 bedrooms and 2 baths. The gorgeous kitchen overlooks the dining room and features beautiful granite countertops. The master suite is nestled in the corner of the home and boasts a spacious master bath and massive walk-in closet. Towards the front of the home, two additional bedrooms share a second bathroom. A two-car garage completes this beautiful 1,266 sq. ft. home. Estimated availability Available Now!
